										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Got gifted a pack of <a href="https://www.copplestonecastings.co.uk/prod.php?prod=351" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Copplestone Castings</strong>&#8216; <strong>wolves</strong></a>. No real prospect of them going on the 12.5mm bases most of the minis are on, so they got treated to the 20mm washers; metals ones, rather than plastic, which give each mini a nice bit of extra heft but makes sticking magnets to the bottom a trickier task.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<figure data-carousel-extra='{&quot;blog_id&quot;:173068755,&quot;permalink&quot;:&quot;https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/02/14/15mm-wolves/&quot;}'  class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
