</figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Very simple to paint: Runic Grey speedpaint over an off-white basecoat, then a slightly watered-down Black Templar contrast paint along the top. My one working red paint with Skeleton Horde contrast paint over the top for the tongues, and the off-white to bring out the teeth.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



