		<title>Another 15mm Giant, or a 28mm Ghoul</title>
		<link>https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/</link>
					<comments>https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Idle Doodler]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 24 Jan 2026 17:35:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[15mm]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[28mm]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Fantasy]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Tabletop Miniatures]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Games Workshop]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Miniatures]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/?p=5561</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[While rummaging around in my box of old miniatures for something to give away in the Tabletop Miniature Hobby Podcast secret santa last month (ended up passing on some Perry Miniatures pieces which had lain untouched for over a decade; the new owner has nearly finished them already), I came across an old Games Workshop &#8230; <a href="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="screen-reader-text">Another 15mm Giant, or a 28mm&#160;Ghoul</span></a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While rummaging around in my box of old miniatures for something to give away in the <strong><a href="https://bedroombattlefields.com/podcast/">Tabletop Miniature Hobby Podcast</a></strong> secret santa last month (ended up passing on some Perry Miniatures pieces which had lain untouched for over a decade; the new owner has nearly finished them already), I came across an old Games Workshop ghoul which I had given a fairly crude sepia wash to be part of the <strong><a href="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2018/01/12/the-cult-of-the-beetle/">Cult of the Beetle</a></strong> and then left collecting dust. Distinct in style from the <strong><a href="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2025/11/08/a-15mm-giant-28mm-troll/">previous giant</a></strong> but still giving off the same vibes as the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1C2Rz_NbP5o" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>animated BFG</strong></a>. </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<figure data-carousel-extra='{&quot;blog_id&quot;:173068755,&quot;permalink&quot;:&quot;https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/&quot;}'  class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-11 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="388" data-attachment-id="5563" data-permalink="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/078-another-giant/" data-orig-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png" data-orig-size="1955,742" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="078 &amp;#8211; Another Giant" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=656" data-id="5563" src="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-5563" srcset="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=1024 1024w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=150 150w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=300 300w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=768 768w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png?w=1440 1440w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant.png 1955w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A couple of layers of Pallid Bone speed paint, then highlighted with Vallejo Stone Grey with a bit off white mixed in. Then some Army Painter Strong Tone dabbed into some nooks and crannies. A fairly quick job; just took forever to get around to doing the ever laborious chore of basing it properly. A shame that I&#8217;d had to rip it from the clear base it had been on, but it&#8217;s better to fit in with the rest of the minis and allow space for magnetising.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>



<figure data-carousel-extra='{&quot;blog_id&quot;:173068755,&quot;permalink&quot;:&quot;https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/&quot;}'  class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-12 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="512" data-attachment-id="5565" data-permalink="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/2026/01/24/another-15mm-giant-or-a-28mm-ghoul/078-another-giant-b/" data-orig-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png" data-orig-size="2528,1265" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="078 &amp;#8211; Another Giant b" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=656" data-id="5565" src="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-5565" srcset="https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=1024 1024w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=2048 2048w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=150 150w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=300 300w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=768 768w, https://therecouldhavebeensnakes.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/078-another-giant-b.png?w=1440 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
